General Nutrition Inc filed aregistration statement with the Securities and ExchangeCommission for a secondary offering of eight mln common shares.    All the shares are being sold by the estate of DavidShakarian, the founder of the company. Kidder, Peabody and CoInc will be the sole manager of the underwriting.    The Shakarian estate owns 25.6 mln shares of GeneralNutrition. There are 33.1 mln shares outstanding. Reuter&#3;